Derek Cecil https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Derek_Cecil 0 Derek Cecil (born January 5, 1973) is an American actor. He played the role of Seth Grayson on the Netflix series House of Cards. He starred in the short-lived series Push, Nevada. He also made many appearances on the series Pasadena. Derek_Cecil ( born January_5_,_1973 ) is an_American_actor .
